<section class="about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-section-inner">
      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <p class="emphasis">Simple. Transparent. Fast.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Create your invoice</strong> — Add line items, tax, due dates. Professional invoices in under 60 seconds.</li>
        <li><strong>Send to your client</strong> — They get an email with a secure payment link and a "Pay Now" button.</li>
        <li><strong>Get paid</strong> — Your client pays via Stripe, PayPal, or cryptocurrency. Payments land in your Payxem wallet.</li>
        <li><strong>Withdraw anytime</strong> — No $150 minimum. No annual fees.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-section-inner">
      <h2>The Important Part</h2>
      <p class="emphasis">We don't hold your money.</p>
      <p>Payxem is invoicing and payment coordination software. We partner with regulated payment processors to handle the actual money movement — you get the simple platform that ties it all together.</p>
      <p>All payments flow through regulated, secure infrastructure. They're licensed, regulated, and trusted by millions of businesses worldwide.</p>
      <p>Payxem coordinates the process. We're not a bank, not a payment processor, not a money service. We're the software layer that makes professional invoicing and payment link creation accessible to everyone.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

